{"tid":443994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南亞女天慈邨被強姦 重案閃電拉26歲本地男","createTime":"2017-10-22T06:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-22T07:12:00.000Z","uid":8129,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3a573faa6e0184e983109a4fcd5d6aab5fc4a0","tid":443994,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:34:46.000Z","msg":"淫魔天水圍強姦南亞女，警方重案組不足12小時擒獲涉案男。昨日上午11時許，一名25歲南亞裔女子，於天喜街天慈邨報警，稱在上址一單位被一名男子強姦。警方接報到場，將女事主送院檢查，經初步調查，案件列強姦，交由元朗警區重案組第3隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n重案組探員翻看現場天眼片段及蒐證後，鎖定一名目標，至昨晚10時30分，於天水圍拘捕一名26歲姓馮男子，他涉嫌「強姦」，帶署通宵扣查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171022/bkn-20171022020040141-1022_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171022%2Fbkn-20171022020040141-1022_00822_001.html&d=9JwYeKXHddSTeQeS7%2B%2BYkcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=319100d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171022/bkn-20171022020040141-1022_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張超雄引入假難民,增加本地市民犯罪率正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcee6c7a4e49d7f33d6c3b424ff329bd4e8beb1e","tid":443994,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:08:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fce86f5d95d8d6bb87d73fc4aedd905b2fe49be7","tid":443994,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T07:12:00.000Z","msg":"重口味到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}